DanRosas was supposed to start at 11:00am CST but he seems to have started half-an-hour early. Can we just assume that the schedule isn't going to reflect reality, aside from maybe order of topics?
He actually started about half an hour late, because HarvesteR was delayed in traffic and so they didn't start until about 10:40 CST.
That's exactly it. Ran a bit late, but things are still going off without a hitch...minus lag.
